ShadowMUD SimulEfun: item_list()

string item_list(mixed items...)

mixed items - can be a string array or a string list

DESCRIPTION
Will return a formated list as string

EXAMPLE
    list_item("one", "two") //returns "one and two"
    list_item("one", "two", "three") //returns "one, two, and three"
    list_item( ({"one", "two"}) ) //returns "one and two"
    list_item( ({"one", "two", "three"}) ) //returns "one, two, and three"

LOCATION
/adm/simul_efun/grammar.c

